data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous home with beautiful curb appeal. It is situated on a cul de sac with a little more than a third of an acre. This home boasts tons of space for living and entertaining. The kitchen has lots of cabinets, built in desk, granite countertops, island, stainless appliances, eat in kitchen and breakfast bar. The large primary suite features a view of the pool along with a relaxing fireplace with a sitting area. The primary bathroom has 2 vanities, jetted tub, separate shower and a large walk in closet. Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms, media and game room, study computer area. 2 of the bedrooms share a jack n jill bathroom. The large backyard with a pool will not disappoint. Mansfield ISD, shopping and restaurants close by. Mansfield National Golf Course and Hawaiian Falls water park are also close by. Garage door is Wi-fi enabled. Fingerprint lock on front door. Wi-fi enabled thermostats.
